{
  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of a city nestled beside a large body of water, all bathed in the vibrant colors of a sunset or sunrise. The sky is a spectacular display of fiery oranges, deep reds, and subtle pinks streaking across the clouds. These clouds are long, wispy, and dramatically angled, creating a dynamic and painterly effect. Below the sky, the city appears as a dense collection of lights and buildings, stretching along the coastline. In the foreground, a hillside covered in lush green vegetation and trees frames the scene. A few houses are visible on the hillside, adding a sense of scale and human presence. The water reflects the colors of the sky, enhancing the overall beauty and tranquility of the image.",
